To setup the project: i.e node project

1.create empty directory

it contains package.json i.e
```
npm init
```


it adds node_modules , package-lock.json , dependencies in package.json that is "express" i.e
```
npm install express
```


it adds dependencies of mongodb i.e
```
npm install mongoose
```



for running the index.js file which is for the node.js i.e
```
node index.js
```

for automatic changes i.e
```
nodemon index.js
```



